      "content": "\u003cdiv class\u003d\"introduction img-head\"\u003e\r\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"header\"\u003e\r\n  \u003cimg src\u003d\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,\u003d\u003d\" alt\u003d\"\" /\u003e\r\n  \u003ch3\u003eEarning Call Report Analytics\u003c/h3\u003e\r\n  \u003c/div\u003e\r\n\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n  \u003ch4\u003eOverview\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n  \u003cp\u003e\r\n  This app is a comprehensive financial analysis tool designed to provide\r\n  users with dynamic visualizations and detailed reports on financial data. It \r\n  enables users to generate various charts, balance sheet tables, and perform \r\n  in-depth financial analysis. With integrated Quality Assurance (QA) processes, \r\n  the application ensures reliability, accuracy, and a seamless user experience.\r\n  \u003c/p\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n  \u003ch4\u003eInput\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n  \u003cp\u003eUsers provide:\u003c/p\u003e\r\n  \u003cul\u003e\r\n  \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e A financial report (\u003ca href\u003d\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1NfheYBXd2ZWnTDY1BqVCedSflj9r8xNq/view?usp\u003dsharing\"\u003eSample Report\u003c/a\u003e) issued by their organization\u003c/li\u003e\r\n  \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Sample or custom queries related to the report they require to be answered\u003c/li\u003e\r\n  \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n  \u003ch4\u003eOutput\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n  \u003cp\u003eThis app delivers:\u003c/p\u003e\r\n  \u003cul\u003e\r\n  \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Visualizations of balance-sheet, cash-flow and related insights derived from the report\u003c/li\u003e\r\n  \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e AI-generated, data-backed summaries and responses to queries you ask based on the uploaded report\u003c/li\u003e\r\n  \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n  \r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n  \u003ch4\u003eBenefits\u00